<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Hipoclorhidria — Sistema Clínico Inteligente</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117;
    --surface: #161b22;
    --surface2: #1c2230;
    --border: #2a3347;
    --text: #e8ecf0;
    --muted: #7a8898;
    --accent: #3b9eff;
    --accent2: #00d4aa;
    --warn: #ff8c42;
    --danger: #ff4d6d;
    --success: #4ade80;
    --clinical: #3b9eff;
    --patient: #ff8c42;
    --radius: 12px;
    --transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
  }
  .mode-patient {
    --accent: #ff8c42;
    --accent2: #ffd166;
    --surface: #1a1510;
    --surface2: #221d15;
    --border: #3a2f1e;
    --bg: #110e08;
  }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
    transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }

  /* ─── HEADER ─── */
  .header {
    position: sticky; top:0; z-index:100;
    background: rgba(13,17,23,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 24px;
    display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    height: 64px;
    transition: background var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
  }
  .mode-patient .header { background: rgba(17,14,8,0.92); }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    color: var(--text);
    display: flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
  }
  .logo-dot {
    width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--accent);
    transition: background var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }
  .mode-toggle {
    display: flex; align-items:center;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 4px;
    gap:2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .toggle-btn {
    padding: 7px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: all var(--transition);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .toggle-btn.active {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(59,158,255,0.4);
  }
  .mode-patient .toggle-btn.active {
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(255,140,66,0.4);
  }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    padding: 64px 24px 48px;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hero-badge span {
    width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%;
    background: var(--accent2);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%,100% { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
    50% { opacity:0.5; transform:scale(0.8); }
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 32px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; justify-content:center; gap:40px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .hero-stat {
    text-align:center;
  }
  .hero-stat .num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px; color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero-stat .label { font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:2px; }

  /* ─── NAV TABS ─── */
  .nav-tabs {
    max-width:960px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; gap:4px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .nav-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
  .tab-btn {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border:none; background:transparent;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size:14px; font-weight:500;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom:-1px;
    white-space:nowrap;
    transition: all var(--transition);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

  /* ─── MAIN CONTENT ─── */
  .main { max-width:960px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px 24px 80px; }
  .section { display:none; animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease; }
  .section.active { display:block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(12px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }

  /* ─── CARDS ─── */
  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .card-header { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .card-icon {
    width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:18px; flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .card h3 { font-size:17px; font-weight:600; }
  .card p { color:var(--muted); line-height:1.7; font-size:14px; }

  /* ─── GRIDS ─── */
  .grid-2 { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:16px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .grid-3 { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap:16px; margin-bottom:24px; }

  /* ─── SECTION TITLES ─── */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing:-0.5px;
  }
  .section-title em { font-style:italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .section-sub { color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:32px; font-size:14px; }

  /* ─── SYMPTOM CHECKER ─── */
  .symptom-grid {
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap:10px;
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .symptom-chip {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:13px;
    transition: all var(--transition);
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    user-select:none;
  }
  .symptom-chip:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .symptom-chip.selected {
    background: rgba(59,158,255,0.1);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .mode-patient .symptom-chip.selected {
    background: rgba(255,140,66,0.1);
    border-color: var(--patient);
    color: var(--patient);
  }
  .symptom-check {
    width:18px; height:18px; border-radius:4px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    flex-shrink:0;
    transition: all var(--transition);
    font-size:11px;
  }
  .symptom-chip.selected .symptom-check {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color:#fff;
  }
  .mode-patient .symptom-chip.selected .symptom-check {
    background: var(--patient);
    border-color: var(--patient);
  }
  .result-box {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    display:none;
  }
  .result-box.show { display:block; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
  .result-label { font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .result-score {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size:48px; color: var(--accent);
    line-height:1;
  }
  .result-text { color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; margin-top:12px; line-height:1.6; }
  .result-actions {
    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:20px;
  }
  .tag-action {
    background: rgba(59,158,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59,158,255,0.3);
    border-radius:6px;
    padding:6px 12px;
    font-size:12px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .mode-patient .tag-action {
    background: rgba(255,140,66,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255,140,66,0.3);
    color: var(--patient);
  }

  /* ─── TIMELINE ─── */
  .timeline { position:relative; padding-left:32px; }
  .timeline::before {
    content:''; position:absolute; left:8px; top:0; bottom:0; width:2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), transparent);
  }
  .timeline-item { position:relative; margin-bottom:32px; }
  .timeline-dot {
    position:absolute; left:-28px; top:4px;
    width:12px; height:12px; border-radius:50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59,158,255,0.2);
  }
  .timeline-phase {
    font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px;
    color: var(--accent); margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .timeline-title { font-weight:600; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .timeline-content { color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; }
  .timeline-pills { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; margin-top:10px; }
  .pill {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:4px 12px;
    font-size:12px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .pill.green { border-color:rgba(74,222,128,0.4); color:var(--success); }
  .pill.yellow { border-color:rgba(255,209,102,0.4); color:#ffd166; }
  .pill.red { border-color:rgba(255,77,109,0.4); color:var(--danger); }
  .pill.blue { border-color:rgba(59,158,255,0.4); color:var(--accent); }

  /* ─── TABLES ─── */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x:auto; margin-bottom:24px; }
  table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px; }
  th {
    text-align:left; padding:10px 14px;
    background:var(--surface2); color:var(--muted);
    font-weight:500; font-size:11px;
    text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  td {
    padding:10px 14px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,51,71,0.5);
    color:var(--text); vertical-align:top; line-height:1.5;
  }
  tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  .badge {
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center;
    padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-size:11px; font-weight:500;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .badge-red { background:rgba(255,77,109,0.15); color:var(--danger); }
  .badge-yellow { background:rgba(255,209,102,0.15); color:#ffd166; }
  .badge-green { background:rgba(74,222,128,0.15); color:var(--success); }
  .badge-blue { background:rgba(59,158,255,0.15); color:var(--accent); }

  /* ─── INFO BOX ─── */
  .info-box {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-left: 4px solid;
  }
  .info-box.warning { background:rgba(255,140,66,0.08); border-color:var(--warn); }
  .info-box.danger { background:rgba(255,77,109,0.08); border-color:var(--danger); }
  .info-box.success { background:rgba(74,222,128,0.08); border-color:var(--success); }
  .info-box.info { background:rgba(59,158,255,0.08); border-color:var(--accent); }
  .info-box .title { font-weight:600; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .info-box p { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.7; }

  /* ─── ANALOGY CARDS (patient mode) ─── */
  .analogy-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .analogy-card::before {
    content:''; position:absolute; top:0; right:0;
    width:120px; height:120px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,140,66,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius:50%;
  }
  .analogy-emoji { font-size:40px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .analogy-card h3 { font-size:20px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .analogy-card p { color:var(--muted); line-height:1.8; font-size:15px; }

  /* ─── DO / DON'T ─── */
  .do-dont { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  @media (max-width:600px) { .do-dont { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
  .do-box, .dont-box {
    border-radius:12px; padding:20px;
  }
  .do-box { background:rgba(74,222,128,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.2); }
  .dont-box { background:rgba(255,77,109,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,77,109,0.2); }
  .do-box h4 { color:var(--success); margin-bottom:12px; font-size:14px; }
  .dont-box h4 { color:var(--danger); margin-bottom:12px; font-size:14px; }
  .do-dont li { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:16px; line-height:1.5; }

  /* ─── HRV GAUGE ─── */
  .hrv-gauge { display:flex; gap:8px; margin-bottom:24px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .hrv-zone {
    flex:1; min-width:100px;
    padding:14px; border-radius:10px;
    text-align:center; cursor:default;
  }
  .hrv-zone .zone-range { font-family:'JetBrains Mono'; font-size:16px; font-weight:500; }
  .hrv-zone .zone-label { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:4px; }
  .hrv-zone .zone-action { font-size:11px; margin-top:8px; line-height:1.4; }

  /* ─── PROTOCOL STEPS ─── */
  .steps { counter-reset:step; }
  .step {
    display:flex; gap:16px; margin-bottom:20px;
    counter-increment:step;
  }
  .step-num {
    flex-shrink:0; width:32px; height:32px;
    border-radius:50%; border:2px solid var(--accent);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--accent);
    margin-top:2px;
  }
  .step-body h4 { font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px; font-size:15px; }
  .step-body p { color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; }

  /* ─── FOOD CARDS ─── */
  .food-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap:12px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .food-card {
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:10px;
    padding:16px;
    text-align:center;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .food-card:hover { border-color:var(--accent); transform:translateY(-2px); }
  .food-card .food-emoji { font-size:28px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .food-card .food-name { font-size:13px; font-weight:500; }
  .food-card .food-benefit { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:4px; }

  /* ─── CHECKLIST ─── */
  .checklist { list-style:none; }
  .checklist li {
    display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px;
    padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(42,51,71,0.4);
    font-size:14px;
  }
  .checklist li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .check-icon { width:20px; height:20px; flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px; }
  .check-icon.ok { color:var(--success); }
  .check-icon.warn { color:var(--warn); }
  .check-icon.fail { color:var(--danger); }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media(max-width:640px) {
    .hero { padding:40px 16px 32px; }
    .hero-stats { gap:24px; }
    .main { padding:24px 16px 60px; }
  }

  /* ─── MONO CODE ─── */
  .mono { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; }
  .code-block {
    background:var(--surface2);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:8px;
    padding:16px;
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
    font-size:12px;
    color:var(--accent2);
    line-height:1.6;
    overflow-x:auto;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }

  /* ─── ALOST SCALE ─── */
  .alost-bar { margin-bottom:24px; }
  .alost-track {
    height:10px; border-radius:10px;
    background:var(--surface2);
    position:relative; overflow:hidden;
    margin:8px 0;
  }
  .alost-fill {
    height:100%; border-radius:10px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--success), #ffd166, var(--danger));
    transition: width 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
  }
  .alost-labels { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); }

  /* Scrollbar */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width:6px; height:6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background:transparent; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background:var(--border); border-radius:3px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header">
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-dot"></div>
    HCl<em style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-style:italic">intel</em>
  </div>
  <div class="mode-toggle">
    <button class="toggle-btn active" id="btn-clinical" onclick="setMode('clinical')">🔬 Clínico</button>
    <button class="toggle-btn" id="btn-patient" onclick="setMode('patient')">🌿 Paciente</button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="hero-section">
  <!-- CLINICAL HERO -->
  <div id="hero-clinical">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span></span>Sistema Omni-Circadiano v4.0</div>
    <h1>Hipoclorhidria —<br><em>Análisis Clínico Profundo</em></h1>
    <p>Protocolo de 20 puntos, 8 pilares y 7 capas de integración clínica para la evaluación y tratamiento funcional de la hipoclorhidria.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">20</div><div class="label">Puntos del protocolo</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">8</div><div class="label">Pilares clínicos</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">7</div><div class="label">Capas de integración</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">3</div><div class="label">Casos clínicos</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- PATIENT HERO -->
  <div id="hero-patient" style="display:none">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span></span>Guía amigable para pacientes</div>
    <h1>Tu estómago<br><em>necesita ayuda</em></h1>
    <p>Aprende qué está pasando en tu cuerpo, por qué te sientes así y qué puedes hacer hoy para empezar a mejorar.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">🔍</div><div class="label">Descubre tus síntomas</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">🥗</div><div class="label">Qué comer y evitar</div></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><div class="num">📅</div><div class="label">Plan paso a paso</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- NAV TABS -->
<nav class="nav-tabs" id="nav-tabs">
  <!-- Clinical tabs -->
  <div id="tabs-clinical" style="display:contents">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('overview')">Visión General</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('symptoms')">Síntomas & Diagnóstico</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('protocol')">Protocolo</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('labs')">Laboratorios</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('timeline')">Línea de Tiempo</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('hrv')">HRV & SNA</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('cases')">Casos Clínicos</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('contraindications')">Contraindicaciones</button>
  </div>
  <!-- Patient tabs -->
  <div id="tabs-patient" style="display:none">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('p-what')">¿Qué me pasa?</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('p-symptoms')">Mis Síntomas</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('p-food')">Qué Comer</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('p-habits')">Hábitos Diarios</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('p-plan')">Mi Plan</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('p-avoid')">Qué Evitar</button>
